The error is: XAMPP Error: MySQL shutdown unexpectedly...

1. Go to your xampp/mysql folder
2. create a copy of the "data" folder (ex: name it, "data_old1")
3. go to your original "data" folder

We need to keep our databases, all we need to delete are the mysql databases.

4. delete the following folders: 
  * mysql
  * performance schema
  * phpmyadmin
  * test

5. delete all the files EXCEPT the "ibdata1"
6. go to xamp/msql/backup folder
7. copy everything inside it EXCEPT the "ibdata1"

8. go back to the xamp/mysql/data folder
9. paste what you just copied
10. run mysql in your xampp control panel agan.
